  "A=30, B=20": "",
  "A=0, B=50": "",
  "A=40, B=0": "",
  "Constraints: 3A + 2B ≤ 120, A + B ≤ 50, A,B ≥ 0. Vertices: (0,0), (40,0), (20,30), (0,50). P = 8A + 6B. P(20,30) = 160+180 = 340 is maximum.": "",
